**Style:** ARRI Alexa (Camera), Low-Key to High-Key transition (Lighting), Handheld to Steadycam (Motion)
**Environment Anchor:**
    *   **Problem:** A bustling, slightly dull city street corner on an overcast morning.
    *   **Solution:** A sophisticated, airy rooftop garden at golden hour, city skyline in distance.

